<title>HONG KONG: Dickson Cons. year net loss HK$1.8 mln.</title>
<headline>Dickson Cons. year net loss HK$1.8 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   0.6 loss  vs 13.1 loss</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	 vs nil</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  2.57 gain vs 19.60 loss</p>
<p>    Net			    1.80 loss vs 40.27 loss</p>
<p>    Turnover		     748.10    vs 882.55</p>
<p>    Company name		 Dickson Construction International</p>
<p>Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  N/A</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   N/A</p>
